          "alts": [],
          "explanation": "<b>～たいなら</b> combines the desire form (～たい) with the contextual conditional (～なら): 'if you want to do X.' 考え方を 正したいなら = 'if you want to correct your way of thinking.' The correct order puts the goal condition first, then the recommendation."
